  <text>
      <body>
        
     
      <div xml:id="Nevergiveallheart"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="freeverse"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
              <l>Never give all the heart, for love</l>
          <l>Will hardly seem worth thinking of</l> 
          <l>To passionate women if it seem</l>
          <l>Certian, and they never dream</l>
          <l>That it fades out from kiss to kiss;</l>
          <l>For everything that's lovely is</l>
          <l>But a breif, dreamy, kind of delight.</l>
          <l>O never give the hearts up to the play</l>
          <l>And who could play it well enough</l>
          <l>If deaf and dumb and blind with love?</l>
          <l>He that made this knows all cost,</l>
          <l>For he gave all his heart and lost.</l>
                 
